 <table-wrap-foot>
  <p>The measures of accuracy were calculated as follows: 
   <table-wrap id="Taba">
    <table frame="hsides" rules="groups">
     <thead>
      <tr>
       <th>
        <bold>Measure</bold>
       </th>
       <th>
        <bold>Formula</bold>
       </th>
      </tr>
     </thead>
     <tbody>
      <tr>
       <td>Sensitivity</td>
       <td>(TP/(TP+ FN)) * 100%)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
       <td>Specificity</td>
       <td>(TN/(FP+TN)) * 100%)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
       <td>Accuracy</td>
       <td>((TP+TN)/(TP+TN+FP+FN))*100%)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
       <td colspan="2">TP = # True Positives; FP = # False Positives; TN=# True Negatives; FN=# False Negatives</td>
      </tr>
     </tbody>
    </table>
   </table-wrap>
  </p>
